ZH: 我今天有很多功课要做。
EN: I have a lot of homework to do today.

ZH: 我昨天晚上花了很长时间做功课。
EN: I spent a long time doing homework last night.

ZH: 她总是非常努力完成自己的功课。
EN: She always works very hard to finish her homework.

ZH: 我们的老师要求我们每天都要完成功课。
EN: Our teacher requires us to finish our homework every day.

ZH: 我的功课太多了，我不知道从哪里开始做。
EN: I have too much homework, I don't know where to start.

ZH: 我们应该把功课放在第一位，不要拖延。
EN: We should prioritize homework and not procrastinate.

ZH: 她喜欢学校的功课，每天都认真完成。
EN: She enjoys schoolwork and completes it diligently every day.

ZH: 我们都在课间时间做功课，以便回家后可以休息。
EN: We do homework during break time so we can relax when we get home.

ZH: 她放学后去图书馆做功课。
EN: She goes to the library to do homework after school.

ZH: 我晚上总是在家里做功课。
EN: I always do homework at home in the evenings.

ZH: 她让我帮忙做功课。
EN: She asked me to help with homework.

ZH: 你完成功课了吗？
EN: Have you finished your homework?

ZH: 我们有一个关于历史的功课要完成。
EN: We have a history assignment to complete.

ZH: 父母会监督孩子们做功课。
EN: Parents will supervise their children doing homework.

ZH: 我们班的功课都非常难。
EN: The homework in our class is very difficult.

ZH: 我喜欢在安静的地方做功课。
EN: I like doing homework in quiet places.

ZH: 兄弟俩通常一起做功课。
EN: The two brothers usually do homework together.

ZH: 孩子们必须每天做功课。
EN: The children have to do homework every day.

ZH: 我们一起做功课，相互帮助。
EN: We do homework together and help each other.

ZH: 明天的功课是什么？
EN: What is the homework for tomorrow?
